<!-- XML - element -->
    XML is case sensitive

    An element can contain:
        ◦ text
        ◦ attributes
        ◦ other elements
        ◦ or a mix of the above
        
        Empty element: <link href=‘http://www.wp.pl’> </link>
        
        <person>
            Definition for a person
            <name>Anna</name>
            <surname >Kowalska</surname>
            with mixed value
        </person>



